<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Mssql - 标签 - w23ta0's blog</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/tags/mssql/</link><description>You got a dream, you gotta protect it.</description><generator>Hugo 0.145.0 &amp; FixIt v0.3.16</generator><language>zh-cn</language><managingEditor>tom920wt@hotmail.com (w23ta0)</managingEditor><webMaster>tom920wt@hotmail.com (w23ta0)</webMaster><lastBuildDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 11:23:13 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://w23ta0.github.io/tags/mssql/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>使用MSSQL远程重启服务器的方法</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20121211-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8mssql%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E9%87%8D%E5%90%AF%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/</link><pubDate>Tue, 11 Dec 2012 13:56:58 +0000</pubDate><author>tom920wt@hotmail.com (w23ta0)</author><guid>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20121211-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8mssql%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E9%87%8D%E5%90%AF%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/</guid><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93/">数据库</category><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/sqlserver/">SQLServer</category><description>&lt;p>单位托管有服务器,或者经常在家里休息时单位服务器出现问题时,相信用远程桌面或&lt;code>pcanywhere&lt;/code>的朋友遇到过莫名其妙断线而不能再连接的情况。这时,如果服务器如果安装有SQL server,则可用如下的方法重启服务器解决。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>本地用SQL server连接上服务器后,在SQL查询工具里执行如下命令:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt"> 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 8
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 9
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">10
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">11
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">12
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">xp_cmdshell &amp;#39;shutdown -r -t 80&amp;#39; 用SQL在80秒后重新启动电脑
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">shutdown -a 取消重新启动
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">shutdown.exe -a 取消关机
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">shutdown.exe -d [p]:xx:yy 列出系统关闭的原因代码。
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">shutdown.exe -f 强行关闭应用程序。
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">shutdown.exe -m \计算机名　控制远程计算机。
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">shutdown.exe -i 显示图形用户界面，但必须是Shutdown的第一个参数。
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">shutdown.exe -l 注销当前用户。
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">shutdown.exe -r 关机并重启。
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">shutdown.exe -t 时间 设置关机倒计时。默认值是 30 秒。
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">shutdown.exe -c &amp;#34;消息内容&amp;#34; 输入关机对话框中的消息内容(不能超127个字符)。&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>远程关闭/重启pcanywhere&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>